Included Files:


README:
        Identification information and a brief overview of the included files.


Makefile:
        Script that includes the default compile of the lab4b executable. It also 
includes clean, which removes all files created the Makefile, check, which runs a 
sanity check on the executable, and dist, which builds the tar.gz file.


lab4b.c:
	C code for lab 4b. It initialized the button and temperature sensor and
reported the temperature every specified period. The temperature could be specified
to either Fahrenheit or Celsius. There was also a log option which would append all outputted data to a specified file.


