References:


- http://www.cplusplus.com/reference/cstdio/fopen/
  Opening and closing files for the --log option.
- https://www.gnu.org/software/libc/manual/html_node/Cleanups-on-Exit.html
  At exit function for closing files for the --log option.
- http://www.mouser.com/catalog/specsheets/Seeed_101020015.pdf
  Converting temperature input into Fahrenheit and Celsius.


